    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major restoration project or a donor car for parts. The engine currently runs but suffers from significant oil leaks and overheating issues, while the transmission shifts roughly. Externally, the body has several areas of rust and the paint is peeling, and the interior shows heavy wear and tear on all surfaces. It is not roadworthy in its current state and will need to be towed.",
      "price": 3800.0,
